        Text::Textile - a Perl implementation of Textile


DESCRIPTION

Text::Textile is a Perl impementation of the Textile formatting language.


DOCUMENTATION

Documentation for this module is available in Textile.pm in POD format.


INSTALLATION

Traditional Perl module installation applies here:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


CONTACT INFORMATION

This module was written by Brad Choate (bradchoate.com), based off the hard
work of Dean Allen (textism.com).


LICENSE

